# platform-security.guard â€” cfn-guard security policy rules
#
# Enforces platform security constraints on all synthesised CloudFormation templates.
# Run: cfn-guard validate -r infra/guard/platform-security.guard -d cdk.out/*.template.json
#
# Rules implemented in TASK-027:
#   - no_wildcard_iam_action      No IAM policies with Action: "*"
#   - no_wildcard_iam_resource    No IAM policies with Resource: "*"
#   - no_public_s3_bucket         No S3 buckets with public access enabled
#   - dynamodb_pitr_enabled       All DynamoDB tables have PITR enabled
#   - dynamodb_kms_encryption     All DynamoDB tables use KMS encryption
#   - dynamodb_deletion_protection Staging/prod tables have deletion protection
#   - lambda_dlq_configured       All Lambda functions have a DLQ configured
#   - lambda_xray_enabled         All Lambda functions have X-Ray tracing enabled
#   - lambda_in_vpc               All Lambda functions are VPC-attached
#
# Implemented in TASK-027.
